Madonna, 64, flaunted her youthful complexion as she took to Instagram to upload a series of pictures with her children. The Queen of Pop, who has been rehearsing for her upcoming 40th anniversary world tour, recently appeared to admit to having had cosmetic surgery. In the wholesome snaps, Madonna could be seen sharing a hug with her daughter Estere,10, who has an identical twin named Stella. One of the singer’s sons, David Banda, 17, stood in the background with an arm around his mum and sister. Madonna’s 17-year-old daughter Mercy James also appeared in the posts, as she sat at the piano in the rehearsal studio. The pop superstar recently appeared to confess she had undergone plastic surgery as she captioned one of her Instagram posts: “Look how cute I am now that swelling from surgery has gone down. Lol.”